The error in your program is due to trying to add a `String` (i.e., "6") to
to a `Number` (i.e., 4). You can solve this issue by converting the second 
value from string to number using `parseNumber()` function. Here's how you 
can fix it:

```tundra
val raw = ["4", "6", "8"];

val first = parseNumber(raw[0]);
val second = parseNumber(raw[1]); // convert the string to number here
val third = parseNumber(raw[2]);

val total = first + second + third;
print(total);
```
